---
title: Smokey Black Bean Chilli with Garlic Rice & Feta
description: Who doesn't love a piping hot bowl of American-style chilli? Sure to leave you feeling satisfied and nurtured, this one's packed with the goodness of veggies and beans, plus aromatic garlic rice and crumbly feta to top it off. Kick your shoes off and dig in!
